  ConfigError.shape: class

  ValidationError: |md
    **ValidationError**

    + expected: str
    + got: str
  |
  ValidationError.shape: class

  # Hardware & Runtime Errors
  DeviceNotFoundError: |md
    **DeviceNotFoundError**
  |
  DeviceNotFoundError.shape: class

  DllLoadError: |md
    **DllLoadError**
    «NEW»

    + dll_name: str
    + original_error: Exception
  |
  DllLoadError.shape: class
  DllLoadError.style.stroke-width: 2

  EngineStateError: |md
    **EngineStateError**

    + current_state: str
  |
  EngineStateError.shape: class

  EngineRuntimeError: |md
    **EngineRuntimeError**
    «NEW»

    + cuda_error: str
  |
  EngineRuntimeError.shape: class
  EngineRuntimeError.style.stroke-width: 2

  # Research & Benchmarking Errors
  BenchmarkError: |md
    **BenchmarkError**

    + benchmark_name: str
  |
  BenchmarkError.shape: class

  BenchmarkTimeoutError: |md
    **BenchmarkTimeoutError**

    + iteration: int
    + timeout_s: float
